snippet.title: Under the Waves - Xbox Booth Game Overview | gamescom 2022
snippet.description:
Under the Waters, lead developer Roan Coffeic shares an overview of Quantic Dream's newest IP, his personal ties to the game, and what fans of the studio can expect.
